        <h3>Countdown to Freedom: Ten Days That Changed South Africa Synopsis</h3>
        <p>Narrated by James Earl Jones, this 90 minute independent documentary chronicles the behind the scenes rebirth of a nation and Nelson Mandela&#39;s<br />
	triumph in South Africa&#39;s first free elections.</p>
